dao层代码 




1.  package com.msb.dao.impl;
2.  import com.msb.dao.EmpDao;
3.  import com.msb.pojo.Emp;
4.  import java.sql.*;
5.  import java.util.ArrayList;
6.  import java.util.Date;
7.  import java.util.List;
8.  /**
9.   * @Author: Ma HaiYang
10.  * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
11.  */
12. public class EmpDaoImpl implements EmpDao {
13.     private String
    url="jdbc:mysql://127.0.0.1:3306/mydb?useSSL=false&useUnicode=true&character
    ncoding=UTF-8&serverTimezone=Asia/Shanghai";
14.     private String username="root";
15.     private String password="root";
16.     @Override
17.     public List<Emp> findAll() {
18.         List<Emp> list =new ArrayList<>();
19.         Connection connection =null;
20.         PreparedStatement pstat=null;
21.         ResultSet resultSet=null;
22.         try {
23.             Class.forName("com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver");
24.             connection = DriverManager.getConnection(url, username,
    password);
25.             pstat = connection.prepareStatement("select * from emp");
26.             resultSet = pstat.executeQuery();
27.             while(resultSet.next()){
28.                 Integer empno=resultSet.getInt("empno");
29.                 Integer deptno=resultSet.getInt("deptno");
30.                 Integer mgr=resultSet.getInt("mgr");
31.                 String ename=resultSet.getString("ename");
32.                 String job=resultSet.getString("job");
33.                 Double sal=resultSet.getDouble("sal");
34.                 Double comm=resultSet.getDouble("comm");
35.                 Date hiredate=resultSet.getDate("hiredate");
36.                 Emp emp =new Emp( empno,  ename,  job,  mgr,  hiredate, 
    sal,  comm,  deptno);
37.                 list.add(emp);
38.             }
39.         } catch (Exception e) {
40.             e.printStackTrace();
41.         }finally {
42.             if(null!=resultSet){
43.                 try {
44.                     resultSet.close();
45.                 } catch (SQLException e) {
46.                     e.printStackTrace();
47.                 }
48.             }
49.             if(null!=pstat){
50.                 try {
51.                     pstat.close();
52.                 } catch (SQLException e) {
53.                     e.printStackTrace();
54.                 }
55.             }
56.             if(null!=connection){
57.                 try {
58.                     connection.close();
59.                 } catch (SQLException e) {
60.                     e.printStackTrace();
61.                 }
62.             }
63.         }
64.         return list;
65.     }
66. }

 




servlet代码 




1.  package com.msb.servlet;
2.  import com.msb.dao.EmpDao;
3.  import com.msb.dao.impl.EmpDaoImpl;
4.  import com.msb.pojo.Emp;
5.  import javax.servlet.ServletException;
6.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebServlet;
7.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet;
8.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
9.  import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;
10. import java.io.IOException;
11. import java.util.List;
12. /**
13.  * @Author: Ma HaiYang
14.  * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
15.  */
16. @WebServlet("/empServlet.do")
17. public class EmpServlet extends HttpServlet {
18.     // dao对象
19.     EmpDao empDao=new EmpDaoImpl();
20.     @Override
21.     protected void service(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse
    resp) throws ServletException, IOException {
22.         // 获取数据
23.         List<Emp> list = empDao.findAll();
24.         // 将数据放入请求域
25.         req.setAttribute("emps", list);
26.         // 请求转发给JSP
27.         req.getRequestDispatcher("showEmp.jsp").forward(req,resp);
28.     }
29. }
